data.description: 4.5+ Acres in sought after Hickory Area of Chesapeake.  This home features 6 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, two en-suite bedrooms (one on each floor) and Family Room with fireplace located just off the large kitchen, excellent for entertaining.  This fully fenced farm is ready for your horses, chickens, goats and gardens with several enclosures, shelters and multiple storage sheds.  Location is convenient to dining, shopping, and entertainment, interstate and North Carolina.      **SELLERS ARE ALLOWING THE ASSUMPTION OF THEIR 2.75% VA LOAN TO ELIGIBLE VA BUYERS, MUST QUALIFY.      **DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS OPPORTUNITY TO OWN A HOME WITH ACREAGE!
